Kenya. 
<taxonomicName authority="Dollman, 1911" authorityName="Dollman" authorityYear="1911" box="[1441,1822,3329,3363]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Acomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="5" pageNumber="602" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="wilsoni" subSpecies="ablutus">A. A.w.ablutusDollman,1911—NyamaNyango,NEwaso</taxonomicName>
Ng’iroRiver,Kenya.
</paragraph>
