<taxonomicName authority="Dollman, 1914" authorityName="Dollman" authorityYear="1914" box="[1441,1827,3447,3481]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Acomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="5" pageNumber="602" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="wilsoni" subSpecies="nubilus">A. A.w. nubilus Dollman, 1914</taxonomicName>
— known only from the type locality in SW Kenya.
